title: Tanz der Vampire - The musical in Stuttgart
description: The Stuttgart audience is delighted: Count von Krolock once again invites them to the ball.

title: The Music of Harry Potter - Live in Concert
description: Experience the film music of Harry Potter live!

title: Starlight Express
description: No other musical connects generations like STARLIGHT EXPRESS. For a sensational 34 years, Andrew Lloyd Webber's masterpiece has been thrilling young and old alike, and only in Bochum.

title: THE WEEKND - After Hours til Dawn Tour
description: Diamond award-winning artist The Weeknd returns to Germany for concerts this summer as part of his 'After Hours til Dawn Tour'!

title: The Hives - The Death Of Randy Fitzsimmons European Tour 2023
description: 30 years after their formation, the Swedish band is not a bit tired and will come to Germany with their new album The Death Of Randy Fitzsimmons in autumn 2023!

title: Kurt Krömer - Die Gönnung steigt
description: Kurt Krömer has written a new program with which he will go on tour starting in the fall of 2022.
location: Strasse zum FEZ 4 (An der Wuhlheide), 12459 Berlin

title: Depeche Mode - Memento Mori World Tour 2023
description: In 2023 Dave Gahan and Martin Gore will go on a world tour under the motto 'Memento Mori' - from May to July several spectacular concerts in Germany are on the schedule.

title: Helene Fischer - LIVE 2023
description: Helene Fischer goes on a big arena tour in 2023 under the motto LIVE 2023 and presents a phenomenal show in cooperation with Cirque du Soleil!

title: SZA - The S.O.S. Tour
description: SZA brings her successful The S.O.S. Tour to Europe! As a special guest Raye has already been confirmed.

title: Disneys DER KÖNIG DER LÖWEN
description: The musical brings the colorful world of Africa with wild animals and the beautiful Serengeti to Hamburg.

title: Renaissance - Beyonce
description: Renaissance (also referred to as Act I: Renaissance) is the seventh studio album by American singer Beyoncé, released on July 29, 2022, by Parkwood Entertainment and Columbia Records.

title: Hazel Brugger - Do you know this woman?
description: Hazel Brugger has not only become famous, but also grown up: In the meantime, Germany's Best Comedienne 2020 is a homeowner, wife and mother.

title: 50 Cent - The Final Lap Tour
description: 50 Cent announces his worldwide The Final Lap tour for next fall in celebration of the 20th anniversary of Get Rich or Die Tryin'!

title: Harry Styles - Love On Tour 2023
description: Harry Styles announces the continuation of his Love On Tour and comes 2023 for the first time on a big stadium tour!

title: P!NK - Summer Carnival 2023
description: P!NK is back: The pop icon is coming to Germany in 2023 for some epic stadium shows!

title: KISS - End of the Road Tour 2023
description: The END OF THE ROAD-World Tour is heading for the last round and brings the legendary hard rockers of KISS to Germany for five final shows!

title: MAMMA MIA! Hamburg
description: After 20 years, the hit musical MAMMA MIA! returned to its German origins in Hamburg in the summer of 2022. With 22 rousing superhits by ABBA such as Dancing Queen, Take a chance on me and, of course, Mamma Mia, the celebrated original tells a summery, witty and loving story about Donna and her daughter Sophie. The result was a furious musical theater delight full of feelings of happiness that even caught the attention of Hollywood. The screen version with stars like Meryl Streep and Pierce Brosnan also won over an audience of millions.

title: Lang Lang - The Disney Book - Live in Concert
description: Superstar Lang Lang is coming to Berlin's Waldbühne in July 2023! With his program The Disney Book, the piano virtuoso will take his audience into a magical fairytale world full of flying carpets and castles made of ice. He invites fans of all ages to an enchanting musical experience of classical music in one of the most beautiful open-air stages in Europe.

title: WWE - Live 2023
description: When athletic wrestling and spectacle combine, the result is unique wrestling shows whose stars bring huge arenas to a boil. The stunts made famous by Hulk Hogan in the 1980s continue to fascinate a wide audience. Even though the shows staged by WWE today follow a script and the winner is already determined before the fight: Impressive moves like chokeslams and flips off the ring perimeter can't be faked and are what make every wrestling show!

title: Hamilton
description: Hamilton the hit musical. Book, Music and Lyrics by Lin-Manuel Miranda. Choreography by Andy Blankenbuehler. Directed by Thomas Kail.
location: Richard Rodgers Theatre, 226 West 46th Street, New York
